        <text><![CDATA[ <p> <strong>Small Business Growth Act </strong></p> <p>This bill increases from $1 million to $2.5 million the limitation on expensing of depreciable business assets. It also increases the asset threshold amount used to reduce the expensing limitation.</p>]]></text>
